title: Wednesday Post Show Pre-Show (03-10-21)
itunes:title: Wednesday Post Show Pre-Show (03-10-21)
description:
Bobby on the time change this weekend and Daylight Savings Time. Bobby addresses how listeners reacted to the Post Show Pre Show now being its own separate thing. Scuba Steve says it’s 50/50. Bobby also on phone anxiety and had to call a friend yesterday and was getting nervous.
